  <brief_title>Ventilator-associated Pneumonia (VAP) and Humidification System</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Analysis of the Incidence of Ventilator-associated Pneumonia Related to the Humidification System: Heat and Moisture Exchanger Versus Heated Humidification</official_title>
