  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine which humidification system is more effective in
      preventing pneumonia in mechanically ventilated patients. The study will compare a heat and
      moisture exchanger versus heated humidification.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
